{"tid":2490840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男生被控刑毀喜茶原判社會服務令200小時 上訴庭今改判更生中心","createTime":"2021-04-16T02:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T02:18:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"267ff9ee96590584f1ed7aa6335212ea28531d0d","tid":2490840,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:06:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15071&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwPaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=dc65f066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15071</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第一庭 #刑期覆核<br />\n#潘兆初高等法院首席法官<br />\n#彭偉昌上訴庭法官 #潘敏琦法官<br />\n👤周(17) #20200513沙田 <br />\n🛑已還押1個月<br />\n<br />\n控罪：刑事損壞<br />\n周手足被控於2020年5月13日，在香港新界沙田沙田正街18號新城市廣場一期4樓408號舖喜茶，損壞2部收銀機的顯示屏及1部八達通處理器，價值共$15,200的資產。 <br />\n<br />\n周手足在2020年12月7日在温紹明署理主任裁判官席前承認控罪，判處200小時社會服務令。律政司不服判刑過輕，遂向高等法院上訴庭申請刑期覆核。 <br />\n2021年3月18日刑期覆核內容<br />\n<br />\n答辯人患有哮喘，法庭在4月1日要求答辯方呈交醫生或診所的醫療報告，顯示答辯人上次就醫的日期和哮喘的情況。詳情見 2021年4月1日刑期覆核內容<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n🛑改判入更生中心🛑"},{"pid":"f419f0919e8cb6601e648597940c6c84dbc21f6e","tid":2490840,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00eeeb9a218004194c2e96a46bd4e6da43c4a960","tid":2490840,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47488445e2e23ca8d6a8fc6def8b5df73a91a20d","tid":2490840,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-1